message: "If you use or reference this framework, please cite it as below."
title: "The GUAN Framework: Cognitive Copilot + Multi-LLM Orchestration Architecture"
abstract: >-
  A file-based, git-native framework for building persistent AI cognitive profiles
  (GUAN Cards v1.1, Challenge Contract Protocol, Tiered Loading, Scaffold-Substitute Test,
  Parallel Session Protocol, Cognitive Collection Protocol) and orchestrating work across
  multiple LLM platforms (Trigger Matrix v1.2, JSON Output Contract, Codex Review Gate,
  70-20-10 Distribution Rule, Patch-Only Delegation). Original research by GUAN, March 2026.
